  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">PANORAMA: Solutions for Healthy Planet Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">PANORAMA &#x2013; Solutions for a Healthy Planet is a unique example of a bottom-up, multi-actor initiative combining a digital platform dedicated to identify and disseminate proven solutions with offline learning and sharing resources and activities (exchange events, trainings, webinars, publications). The current thematic areas include Protected Areas, Marine and Coastal, Ecosystem based Adaptation, Agriculture and Biodiversity and Business Engagement. In that way PANORAMA is promoting solutions that demonstrate how well protected biodiversity and well managed ecosystems help address societal challenges, increase resilience and adaptation to climate change and thereby achieve development benefits.</narrative>
  </description>
